data.text:
Pay It Forward

A series of freeway car accidents leads to a catastrophic overpass collapse that endangers the lives of civilians and members of the 118.

Love is in the Air

A wedding proposal tragically intersects with a bank robbery; a bride is literally stuck on her way to the altar; Athena talks a victim through her grief; Buck finds a surprise visitor on his doorstep.

Mixed Feelings

The 118 face emergencies at a spin class and a hair salon; a husband and wife couple find themselves in a compromising position; Buck discovers new cognitive abilities; Hen and Karen find out Denny has been seeing his biological father.

Full Moon

A full moon keeps the crew busy with some of the craziest calls yet, as Athena investigates a potential home invasion and faces off against a rabid criminal.
